AutoPreferences - Class in com.ethanruffing.preferenceabstraction
This class provides a layer of abstraction over the possible methods for storing preference data.
AutoPreferences(Class<?>) - Constructor for class com.ethanruffing.preferenceabstraction.AutoPreferences
Constructs a new preferences tracker for the given class, defaulting to the system's native preferences storage system if no higher priority type is found.
AutoPreferences(Class<?>, ConfigurationType) - Constructor for class com.ethanruffing.preferenceabstraction.AutoPreferences
Constructs a new preferences tracker for the given class, forcing use of the specified storage system.
